            <p class="newsletter-title">Legislative Summer Study Committees Announced</p>
            <p>On Thursday the Legislative Council met to discuss topics for interim study committees this summer.
                <a href="http://library.constantcontact.com/download/get/file/1109130244637-120/2013+Summer+Study+Topics.pdf" target="_blank" class="newsletter-inline">This resolution</a> describes the specific
